The paper focuses on object tracking using hyperspectral images, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of material information and feature representation is also related to machine learning (cs.MM), information retrieval (cs.IR), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves the use of correlation filters, which is a technique commonly used in machine learning and computer vision (cs.LG).
